visualeditor-help-link:
{{optional}}

This is the page title with interwiki link of the [[:mw:Help:VisualEditor/User guide|VisualEditor user guide in mediawiki.org]].

If the user guide is translated to your language there, you can put a link to the translated user guide here. Just copy the English string without "Special:MyLanguage" and add a slash and your language code in the end. For example, for Japanese write "mw:Help:VisualEditor/User guide/ja".
